<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmi:id="-mZfAV7RcWJlp5idlHzeEcA" name="Manage problems,_Xpd5gP_AEdqtbrr0B1TG-A" guid="-mZfAV7RcWJlp5idlHzeEcA" authors="Easy-Tour" changeDate="2017-07-24T22:47:39.671-0300" version="1.0.0">
  <keyConsiderations>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Esta tarefa está focada na resolução de problemas.&#xD;
&lt;/p></keyConsiderations>
  <sections xmi:id="_LCxqQAB6EduSVaTQTBfIHA" name="Be aware of the problem" guid="_LCxqQAB6EduSVaTQTBfIHA">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The daily meeting is the ideal moment to detect problems a team may be struggling with. It can even allow to&#xD;
    immediately solve through the team collaboration. However:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Urgent problems can show up in between 2 daily scrums&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        and above all, problem solving is not perform during the meeting (unless solution is trivial)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Following up on a problem reporting, for instance during a daily scrum,&amp;nbsp;cause and impacts on the project must be&#xD;
    identified. A best practice is a informal chat initiated by the &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../Scrum/roles/ScrumMaster_FB66563.html&quot; guid=&quot;_t1K9kPpYEdqsc-f87sBK8A&quot;>ScrumMaster&lt;/a>,&amp;nbsp;with the&#xD;
    problem reporter.&#xD;
&lt;/p></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_PIKyUAB6EduSVaTQTBfIHA" name="Making decisions on action plan" guid="_PIKyUAB6EduSVaTQTBfIHA">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Identifying possible solutions.&lt;br />&#xD;
     A meeting with managers is scheduled if problems with the project can't be easily solved or need a management&#xD;
    decision.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot; href=&quot;./../../Scrum/roles/ScrumMaster_FB66563.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;_t1K9kPpYEdqsc-f87sBK8A&quot;>ScrumMaster&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;must try to solve problems as soon as possible, in order not to&#xD;
    disturb team's progress.&#xD;
&lt;/p></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>&lt;p>&#xD;
    O objetivo é eliminar os problemas experimentados pela equipe para que ele possa se concentrar em seus objetivos reais.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
